Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_gnd_net(25.10)                                        init_gnd_net(25.10)

Name
       init_gnd_net

Syntax
         init_gnd_net <list_of_nets>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies  the  list  of  global  ground  nets used in the design. This
       global variable replaces the previous  rda_Input(ui_gndnet)  configura-
       tion file variable.

Example
              * The  following command specifies VSS as the ground net used in
                the design.

                set init_gnd_net {VSS}

Related Information
              * init_design

